OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1782325131
OL,3,CHospital declares critical incident as
OL,4,Cheat causes cooling systems to fail
OL,6,FA critical incident has been declared
OL,7,Fat the Queen Alexandra Hospital in
OL,8,FPortsmouth after the extreme heat
OL,9,Fcaused some of their cooling units to
OL,10,Ffail, leading to "elevated
OL,11,Ftemperatures" in a number of areas
OL,12,Facross the hospital.
OL,14,FThe hospital said some planned care
OL,15,Fand appointments have been cancelled
OL,16,Funtil the issues have been resolved.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
