PN,38202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1782325131
OL,3,CHospital declares critical incident as
OL,4,Cheat causes cooling systems to fail
OL,6,FThe failure to the cooling units has
OL,7,Faffected the hospital's digital
OL,8,Fsystems and critical clinical
OL,9,Fservices, including theatres, cardiac
OL,10,Fcatheter laboratories (cath labs), and
OL,11,Fdiagnostic scanning facilities.
OL,13,FThey insist patients and staff remain
OL,14,Fsafe, but said engineers are on site
OL,15,Fdoing everything they can to get
OL,16,Fsystems back up and running again.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1782325131
OL,3,CHospital declares critical incident as
OL,4,Cheat causes cooling systems to fail
OL,6,FMark Orchard, Deputy Chief Executive
OL,7,Fand Chief Financial Officer,
OL,8,FPortsmouth Hospitals University NHS
OL,9,FTrust, said: "We would like to
OL,10,Freassure our patients and communities
OL,11,Fthat despite the current challenges,
OL,12,Fessential and emergency services
OL,13,Fremain available for anyone who needs
OL,14,Fthem.
OL,16,F"The unprecedented pressures created
OL,17,Fby the current heatwave, combined with
OL,18,Fthe failure of a number of our chiller
OL,19,Funits, have led to significant
OL,20,Fdisruption across several of our
OL,21,Fservices.
OL,26,@xD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
