OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1782325131
OL,3,CHospital declares critical incident as
OL,4,Cheat causes cooling systems to fail
OL,6,F"Our teams are working hard to repair
OL,7,Fthe affected equipment, restore
OL,8,Fsystems safely and ensure we continue
OL,9,Fto provide safe care for our patients."
OL,11,FPatients who are still attending
OL,12,Fappointments are being asked to limit
OL,13,Fthe number of people they bring, and
OL,14,Fensure they take plenty of water as
OL,15,Fthe hospital is very hot.
OL,26,@qD@gO]
